title: 125: The Trader Joe's Holiday Haul Episode!
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Holiday Haul Episode!
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Jamie & Mikey are trying food finds from TJ’s like cauliflower stuffing, cranberry orange relish, boozy chocolate truffles, Hasselback potatoes, almond nog, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the find of all finds, a 14-calorie chocolate cookie stick! This is truly the don’t-miss episode of the year, as every find received an 8 or higher on Lisa’s rating scale! So what are you waiting for?? Press play now and then when you’re done, jump on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: ‘Tis the season for taste testing great holiday finds from Trader Joe’s!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
